word:
To the poor, sin-sick soul repeat the Saviour's invitation: "Come to me, all ye that labor and are heavy laden, and I will give you rest. Take my yoke upon you, and learn of me; 
                                                                           233
for I am meek and lowly in heart, and ye shall find rest unto your souls. For my yoke is easy, and my burden is light." There is true joy in learning of Christ.
